what I did:

1. Translate and scale the image to take approximately .25 of the screen.
2. re-scale and display image in the middle of the window.
3. use keypress:

	x,X -  y,Y - z,Z: Rotate negatively or positively in this axis 
	q,a,s,d: Translate the object by 1 pixel per update
	h,H - w,W: Scale the height/width negatively or positively
	
4.load a font from bin. and draw it use myfont.
